message: "If you use SkillCurrent or its data compilation, please cite it as below."
title: "SkillCurrent"
abstract: >-
  Task-level analysis of how AI reshapes work, combining the O*NET occupational
  taxonomy, Eloundou (2024) theoretical exposure scores, Microsoft and Anthropic
  empirical AI-usage data, government employment statistics, and longitudinal
  capability measures into workforce-planning intelligence.
